<detailText grammarName="coremedia-richtext-1.0"><div xmlns="http://www.coremedia.com/2003/richtext-1.0" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><p>We are sorry to hear that you are experiencing problems. Our website has been tested and is working with all standard browsers:<br/></p><ul><li><a xlink:href="https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/new/" xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple">Mozilla Firefox </a>(latest version)</li><li><a xlink:href="http://windows.microsoft.com/en-us/internet-explorer/download-ie" xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple">Microsoft Internet Explorer</a> 8, 9, 10 and 11</li><li><a xlink:href="https://www.google.com/intl/en/chrome/browser/" xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple">Google Chrome</a> (latest version)</li><li><a xlink:href="http://www.apple.com/safari/" xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple">Apple Safari</a> (latest version)</li></ul><p>Please use one of these supported standard browsers and/or update your browser to the latest available version.</p><p>If you continue to have problems, please get in touch with our customer service at <a xlink:href="mailto:customer-service@perfect-chef.com" xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple">customer-service@perfect-chef.com</a>.</p></div></detailText>
